trans-unit.source: Returns a collection of all <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptReference"></xref> controls that are defined in a Web page's <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptManager"></xref> control and <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Restituisce una raccolta di tutti <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptReference"> </xref> controlli definiti in una pagina Web <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptManager"> </xref> controllo e <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy"> </xref> controlli.

trans-unit.source: The collection that is returned includes framework scripts that are sent automatically to the client to support AJAX functionality such as the <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager> and <xref:System.Web.UI.UpdatePanel> control.
trans-unit.target: La raccolta che viene restituita include gli script del framework che vengono inviati automaticamente al client per supportare la funzionalità AJAX, ad esempio il <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager>e <xref:System.Web.UI.UpdatePanel>controllo.</xref:System.Web.UI.UpdatePanel> </xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager>

trans-unit.source: When you use the GetScriptReferences method, be aware of the following guidelines: - Script references with the same <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference.Name%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference.Assembly%2A> properties are removed as duplicates.
trans-unit.target: Quando si utilizza il metodo GetScriptReferences, tenere presenti le linee guida seguenti:-riferimenti agli Script con lo stesso <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference.Name%2A>e <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference.Assembly%2A>proprietà vengono rimossi come duplicati.</xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference.Assembly%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference.Name%2A>

trans-unit.source: - Script references with the same <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference.Path%2A> are not removed as duplicates at design time.
trans-unit.target: -Riferimenti agli script con lo stesso <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference.Path%2A>non vengono rimossi in fase di progettazione come duplicati.</xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference.Path%2A>

trans-unit.source: However, they are removed as duplicates at run time.
trans-unit.target: Tuttavia, vengono rimossi come duplicati in fase di esecuzione.

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ResolveClientUrl%2A> method is used to return a fully qualified URL for the <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference.Path%2A> property of script references.
trans-unit.target: -La <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ResolveClientUrl%2A>metodo viene utilizzato per restituire un URL completo per il <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference.Path%2A>proprietà dei riferimenti agli script.</xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference.Path%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ResolveClientUrl%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The script references in the returned collection are cloned versions of the original script references and therefore cannot be modified in designer code by using this collection.
trans-unit.target: -I riferimenti a script nella raccolta restituita sono versioni clonate i riferimenti a script originale e pertanto non può essere modificati nel codice della finestra di progettazione tramite questa raccolta.
